title: Logic Power Rechargable Kit 27mg 5pk
description: Logic Power refill packs come with two pre-filled e-liquid cartridges inside, each providing up to 300 vapor puffs. The refills attach to the battery with a simple, secure twist & lock system to ensure reliable vapor production and a satisfying experience every time.  Available in:  Tobacco: Keep it classic with the original tobacco flavor. (27 mg/ml)  Menthol: Keep it fresh with a hint of minty flavor. (27 mg/ml)  Cherry: Taste the joy with a hint of cherry. (27 mg/ml)
